Var[X] = E[(X - E[X])'(X - E[X])] = E[X'X - X'E[X] - E[X]'X + E[X]'E[X]]
$$
$$
= E[X'X] - E[X]'E[X] = 
E\left[
\begin{pmatrix}
X_1 & X_2
